## The 128 Routing Configurations

The core innovation is a **combinatorial content matrix**. Every generation request is a combination of:

| Dimension | Options (Count) | Details |
|-----------|-----------------|---------|
| **Post Type** | Text Basic, Article (2) | Text = ~150 words. Article = 300-500 words. |
| **Purpose** | Breakdown, Announcement, Money Math, ID-Challenge (4) | Each maps to a different directive file with specific writing instructions |
| **Visual Aspect** | None, Image, Video, Carousel (4) | Determines if/what visual asset is generated |
| **Aspect Ratio** | 1:1, 4:5, 16:9, 9:16 (4) | Controls image dimensions |

**2 × 4 × 4 × 4 = 128 distinct generation configs**

